<section xmlns="http://xml.house.gov/schemas/uslm/1.0" style="-uslm-lc:I80" id="id79f09f14-6992-11f1-ab3f-8b4c043f8cd5" identifier="/us/usc/t16/s4603"><num value="4603">§ 4603.</num><heading> Administrative services</heading><content>
<p style="-uslm-lc:I11" class="indent0">The Secretary of the Interior shall provide such facilities, administrative services, personnel, and support to the TPIA Program as the Secretary determines is necessary and appropriate.</p>
</content><sourceCredit id="id79f09f15-6992-11f1-ab3f-8b4c043f8cd5">(<ref href="/us/pl/101/628/tXI/s1104">Pub. L. 101–628, title XI, § 1104</ref>, <date date="1990-11-28">Nov. 28, 1990</date>, <ref href="/us/stat/104/4502">104 Stat. 4502</ref>.)</sourceCredit>
</section>
